■■■ seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_state ■■■

seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_state отображается в ситуации входящего звонка, момент между тем как юзер делающий звонок его инициировал и когда продавец принимающий звонок возьмет трубку.

✠ tables

                                       codename:                                  type:                  designation:             location:  interaction:
s2) ┌─────┬──[seller_shop_call_phone_incoming                          ]  [section_lev2       ]                                    [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ] 
----│     └┬─[seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_header                   ]  [section_lev3       ]                                    [ 🡅 ✜ ]     [ no  ] 
----│      └ [seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_header_label             ]  [label              ]  [ "Голосовая связь"         ]     [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ]
----└┬┬┬┬┬┬┬─[seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main                     ]  [section_lev3       ]                                    [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ] 
---- ││││││└ [seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_info                ]  [label              ]  [ "... входящий звонок ..." ]     [ 🡅 ✜ ]     [ no  ] 
---- │││││└─ [seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_avatar              ]  [frame              ]                                    [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ]
---- ││││└── [seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_action              ]  [label              ]  [ "звонит:"                 ]     [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ]
---- │││└─── [seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_caller              ]  [label              ]  [ { string }                ]     [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ]

---- ││└───┬─[seller_shop_call_phone_context___________________________]  [section_lev4+button]                                    [ ✜ ✜ ]      

---- │└───── [seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_arrow               ]  [icon               ]                                    [ ✜ ✜ ]     [ no  ]
---- └───┬┬──[seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_buttons             ]  [section_lev4       ]                                    [ 🡇 ✜ ]     [ no  ]
----     │└┬─[seller_shop_call_phone_incoming_main_buttons_reject      ]  [button             ]                                    [ ✜ 🡄 ]     [ yes ]
